FBIS3-28492 "dreas026_c_94020" FBIS-EAS-94-026 Document Type:Daily Report 8 Feb 1994 North Korea Kim Il-song Sends Greetings to Finnish President SK0802105994 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1041 GMT 8 Feb 94 SK0802105994 Pyongyang KCNA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Pyongyang, February 8 (KCNA) -- President Kim Il-song of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea today sent a message to Martti Ahtisaari congratulating him upon his election as president of the Republic of Finland. In the message he expressed the belief that the friendly and cooperative relations between the two countries would further develop, and wished the Finnish president success in his work for the prosperity of the country.
